descriptionHtml:
BitRabbit Exchange - Crypto Trading APP



BitRabbit Crypto Trading APP is a free cryptocurrency transaction APP for mobile phone. It's easy and secure. You can use it to buy bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies in an easy way!



Buy bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies easily

Trade bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies smoothly on BitRabbit APP. BitRabbit APP uses world class matching engine with a matching speed reaching over 1.4 million transactions per second. This allows multiple markets and trading pairs to be able to trade at the same time, providing smooth experience to its users.



BitRabbit Crpto Trading APP supports different types of crypto assets, and will continue to launch more quality projects and cryptocurrencies. The APP supports all the mainstream cryptocurrencies, such as bitcoin(BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCHABC), Ethereum (ETH), Ethereum Classic (ETC), EOS, Ripple (XRP), Litecoin (LTC), TrueUSD (TUSD), Tether (USDT), USD Coin ( USDC) and other cryptocurrencies.



Graph and transaction tools

Easily track your digital assets portfolio, check your account and trade in real time. Access tools and real-time prices anytime in an easy way.



Security first

We adopt most advanced security protocal to guarantee your assets staying protected all the time. Provide security guarantee for assets with multiple layers, allow users to securely deposit and trade cryptocurrencies. We will regularly update BitRabbit Crypto Trading APP. Please update your APP in time.



Quality customer service support

We have professional customer service team. No matter you are a professional trader or a newbie, you can enjoy our professional service anywhere anytime. You can also have real-time chat on the APP now! If you have any questions about our Crypto Trading APP, please contact us in our telegram group( https://t.me/bitrabbit_en).



[About BitRabbit]
※ BitRabbit Mission: devoted to providing the most professional, transparency and secure one-station service to users in Blockchain assets industry.

※ BitRabbit has millions of registered users from over 200 countries and regions in the world.

※ BitRabbit official website: www.bitrabbit.com / www.bitrabbit.io



[Product Feature]
※ Support the transaction of various currencies: LTC/BTC、ETH/BTC、BCH/BTC、ETC/BTC、BTC/USDT、LTC/USDT、ETH/ USDT、BCH/ USDT、ETC/ USDT

※ Real-time price

※ Professional K-line graph, index analysis

※Flexible transaction ways: fixed price transaction, market price transaction

※ Quick deposit and withdrawal

※ Multi-language services

※ Convenient assets search
